Module de.sft.mq.rc
Package de.s42.mq.loaders.obj.parser

Interface ObjParserListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
ObjLoader, ObjParserBaseListener
public interface ObjParserListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by ObjParserParser.
